Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if the Crimson Night doesn't come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it really all right for me to come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Saeko's payday is everyones' payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean! But I'll come along since you said so.{loosely TLed}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Eat up, eat up! Eat it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I've had grilled meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sae...ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeko!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, Saeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeko...
