Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-san, who are you? Are you one of the black knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have tested you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... rapidly growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one who bears our hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dead!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shred all of your bonds into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world did Yukiko go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invidia came prepared to blow herself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-You all should die...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-It disappeared... My powers of destruction...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is willing to die to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our unity is being put to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't cooperate now, we will die.{Jibun no haku ni midare ha soku shi ni tsunagaru}{asa: basically, they're playing tennis and if they don't cooperate, they will slap each other with their tennis racket?}{edited to reflect asa's summarization ~MMC}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were looking for you. Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your clothes... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have awoken your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please defeat the demons with that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who awoke the demons is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the only one who can defeat the demons is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Shiori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, defeat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mansion is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superbia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master of the Aeon's Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the Crimson Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we take lives, then we can also live between both worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not even in the Crimson Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could Superbia have...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai. You should accept what has happened and promptly assess the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai has lost himself to his own anger and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry up, defeat Superbia and stop Takahisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Kusukabe girl one of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to make you bring her out, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superbia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking this enormous energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who is Takahisa-senpai fighting against?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko, I'm gonna leave Takahisa to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kukuri and I will go to Superbia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For friends and for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something's strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this uneasiness?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kashagiri Hiromitsu and Kannagiri Nagamitsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kusakabe clan must have fallen far to have entrusted them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, this person has incredible skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back me up.{josei as in reinforcements, not girls ~MMC}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master of the Aeon's Eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have prepared a different oppenent for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the Black Knights we defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superbia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusukabe Misao !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you, Misao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Kusakabe's greatest Onmyouji become a Black Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to fight against ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect Avaritia-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Misao Kusukabe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She truly is a legendary warrior.{\i0}{tlced}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I commend you for instantly knowing to step back{shyunji ni chikara no sao satotte shirizoita koto} from realizing the difference in our powers.{homete yaru}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, for changing your strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're prepared to strike me down,{ayauchi kakugo to nareba}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't afford to make a single mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dedicate this life of mine for my friends and for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such tremendous energy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kakeru has his hands full.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why hasn't Kukuri come?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yukiko hasn't returned yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeko had...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko had raised me up until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She raised me, who was thrown away because of these powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a hopeless guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Saeko isn't around, I'll go insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a Black Knight. It's an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't stop this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents, and my own horrific destructive impulses...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This demonic rampaging fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later, I'm gonna lose control of myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For our friends and for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Takahisa-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Crimson Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two magic circles at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's outside fighting with the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, Shiori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are going to interfere with his growth, I will put you to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he is right now, he is able to protect himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can lose against those puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun is all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's fine even if I don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't guarantee that everyone else is fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. As long as Kakeru-kun is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiori-chan. Won't you have a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go pour some!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless. I can see through your attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad. It's going to become dangerous if she keeps wearing me down like this.{\i0}{ayauchi sura ayaui}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Kakeru-kun and I were raised in the same facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun has been so kind to me ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was always by side, protecting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was then taken in by my current parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru started to live alone and joined the same high school as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun and I have always been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always. Now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love how fairy-tales end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"And so the two of them lived happily ever after."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only this strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did expect a bit more out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see the end of the Kusakabe discipline coming near.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just need one moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can find an opening for just one moment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:19:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ask for your protection and for the destruction of my enemies.{goshinhateki to tomo ni}{needs heavy check here for the chant} {kazaigonazukotoukou}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call upon the god of fire and the flaming chariots to send my enemies into the depths of Hell!{kamikakusu totsukanu gotoku} {honamusubi kasha rairai} {enrainiokuren}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall put everything into this attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katentsuishou!{katensuisha}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kashagiri is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playtime ends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You drank the blood of Kusakabe, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave it at this for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as for "friends and for tomorrow"... I have destroyed all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Ministry of the Index Librorum Prohibitorum{I believe this may be the name of the city} detected an evil disturbance and dispatched me here to Emegaoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the Holy Ministry of the Index Librorum Prohibitorum?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was made in order to seal the calamity that will bring absolute destruction to the world.{sekai ni wazawai wo nasu majutsu kotogotoku horoboshi}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's greatest magical organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're a magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are also.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Knights, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not ordinary magicians, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are disciples that have once been dispatched by the Holy Ministry of the Index Librorum Prohibitorum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the ones that fought to bring an end to the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you saying that the Black Knights are actually fighting for justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Misuzu-san is more familiar with Superbia, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are worlds apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even a match for Kusakabe Misao .
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed Takahisa-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.73,0:24:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed him with these hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.45,0:24:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa... died?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.21,0:24:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"For friends and for tomorrow"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.84,0:24:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have destroyed all of it.{\i0}
